<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٢٢١٣ -<span class="c5"> قَالَ مَعْمَرٌ:</span> وَقَالَ قَتَادَةُ: <span class="c2">«أَصْلُ الشَّجَرَةِ فِي طَرَفِهَا النَّارُ»</span> ,<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> " فَذَلِكَ قَوْلُهُ: <span class="c3">{جَذْوَةٍ مِنَ النَّارِ}</span> <span class="c4">[القصص: ٢٩]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>